# Keeps apps/web/public/ present so Dockerfile.web `COPY apps/web/public` never fails.
# Policy (this project, single-tenant): logo.png + favicons ARE committed here so fresh
# clones and CI builds render correctly. logo.png is used by AppSidebar, the login page,
# and the PDF templates (getLogoDataUrl in apps/api/src/pdf/pdf-templates/logo.ts).
# Do NOT commit generated documents (*.pdf) — gitignored, since public/ is served without auth.
